---
title: Carb Smart Ground Pork and Mushroom Stir-Fry with Sesame Bulgur
description: Bulgur is a sneaky choice for this Asian-inspired dinner. Adding more whole grain nuttiness to this dish works so well with earthy mushrooms and crunchy peas.
